      <div class="msgContentFrame">Its pretty hard to say at this point exactly how the jobs will change as we reach later game... <br /> <br />Just by looking at the abilities the Lancer gets however, it appears that it is a DD/Support character... As for the 'missing' a lot... I used to feel the same- until I learned Feint (R20)... and now I actually WANT to miss.... read up on that ability!! <br /> <br />Also, marauder and lancer are very different... sure they both are melee... but you may want to look a bit more into the abilties that each one offers in order to gain some insight into their differences...<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Maverik <br />Paradise Oblivion <br />75SMN/41WHM/45BRD/37RNG/75COR <br />Maverick Hawkeye. Kashuan.</div></div>
